ClientResponses.Response: Hey, during the recent recipe change, micro ground coffee was added to NESCAFÉ Gold Blend. This is non-soluble coffee and gives you a similar experience to that of a barista made coffee! We're sad you're not enjoying the new blend but thanks for letting us know.

Results.ReviewText: My wife and I have been drinking Gold blend for years. The new style jar has a different taste of coffee to the older one. I find it harsher and it leaves a residue at the bottom of the cup a bit like badly filtered coffee.
Results.Title: Not like the original

Results.ReviewText: Advised to cut down on my coffee intake and was not happy about it. However, when I finally found Gold Blend Decaff I was able to happily subsitute it for my regular brew. Was able to forget it was decaff and just enjoy it.
Results.Title: Surprisingly good!

Results.ReviewText: Having struggled to fine a de-caff that was equal in taste to a regular full-caff I was delighted when I decided to give Nescafe Gold Decaff a go. Is more than equal to other regular coffees and is a regular in my shopping
Results.Title: Equal great taste

Results.ReviewText: As a drinker of decaff coffee, I find most brands lack the flavour I crave. Nescafe gold blend decaff is flavourful, rich and smooth. This coffee suits me perfectly and is also good value compared with other decaff brands.
Results.Title: Who could want more

Results.ReviewText: Had a mug of coffee at my brothers and commented on how tasty it was compared to normal they said they were trying a different one and showed me the jar. That's me converted, next time I go shopping I will be buying a jar
Results.Title: Will buy this from now on

Results.ReviewText: I only drink decaf so I'm always on the look out for a great tasting blend, and I absolutely love this addition to the Nescafe family.  Strong enough without being overpowering, to give a well balanced blend to the coffee
Results.Title: Delicious decaf

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe Gold Blend Decaff is always my first choice when I need a hot drink in the evening. All the taste and flavour of the original Gold Blend but without the caffeine - a drink to enjoy at any time of the day or night.
Results.Title: Same great taste but without the caffeine

Results.ReviewText: I gave up with decaf after many brands didn't live up to expectation, packaging was very appealing on this one and original gold blend is a favourite, am so glad I tried it, in my opinion its the best decaf on the market.
Results.Title: Best decaf I have tried

Results.ReviewText: I wanted to move to a decaf option without any loss of flavour, so I could enjoy a coffee in an evening without a sleepless night. No compromise on taste here, a lovely smooth flavour and perfect aroma to end the evening
Results.Title: Smooth and sleek

Results.ReviewText: Trying to reduce the amount of caffeine I have but cannot do without my coffee. And it HAS to be Nescafe. Therefore, I tried the GOLD BLEND DECAFF and its is gorgeous, smooth, soft but strong, just perfect for my taste.
Results.Title: Great HEALTHY coffee

Taste is rich and full bodied finally a decaff that doesn't compromise on taste
Good value for money, up there with shop bought filter coffee's.

Results.ReviewText: As a coffe lover I enjoy drinking coffee throughout the day to keep me going. Nescafé decaf is perfect for the evening when I relax and want the taste of great coffee without the caffeine to keep me up all night.
Results.Title: Perfect for my bedtime fix!

Results.ReviewText: I am disappointed, it isn't as good as it was. I was surprised to find sludge in the bottom of my mug when I finished the drink. I have been drinking Nescafe Gold Decaf for years, but am looking for a replacement

Results.ReviewText:
I bought this as I really liked the regular Gold.
 Despite being Decaff, it has all the flavour and smoothness I was hoping for. Some decaffs are tasteless, but this is proper coffee! Tasty and rich in flavour.
Results.Title: Really delicious.

Results.ReviewText: Always have this in stock at home as I know it's safe to drink before bedtime. some evenings I just want to enjoy a mug of coffee and I know my favourite will keep me awake so this decaff is perfect alternative.
Results.Title: love it!

Results.ReviewText: I purchased the decaf coffee a couple of weeks ago to drink at work to help me cut down on my caffeine intake and I have been pleasantly surprised at the great flavour of this coffee I would definitely recommend

Results.ReviewText: Encouraged to try new Gold Decaff by my daughter. Flavour and aroma greatly improved. Have drunk Goldblend Decaff for a long time now. But am very pleased with improved product. Much smoother taste and texture.

Results.ReviewText: I`ve been drink this for quite some time it is a pleasant cupper each day as I would recommend to any one who would like a nice cupper each day compared some cheap ones on the market these days so I thumbs up.

Results.ReviewText: I WAS LOOKING FOR A DIFFERENT COFFEE FROM THE ONE I USUALLY BUY AND THOUGHT I WOULD TRY THIS ONE. MY HUSBAND SAID IT WAS THE BEST COFEE HE HAD TASTED IN A LONG TIME. LOVELY RICH TASTE WITHOUT BEING TOO STRONG.

Results.ReviewText:
At last a decaff that is actually worth buying. It is rich, smooth and tastes of coffee, what more do you want?
Is it perfect? No. But it is pretty close.
So give it a try and see how you think it compares.
Results.Title: Finally, a decaff worth buying

Results.ReviewText: Gold Blend Decaf manages to keep the rich taste of the coffee without the caffeine. It has been perfect for me in the evenings when I still like to enjoy a good tasting coffee but not lose any sleep over it.

Results.ReviewText: My doctor told me recently that I had to cut down on my caffeine intake. So I thought I would try a Nescafe one, so glad I did. It was smooth, rich in flavour, just what the doctor ordered (pardon the pun).

Results.ReviewText: I bought this as I only drink decaf and it have such a lovely rich smell and flavour.  I even gave it to my friend who is a hardened coffee drinker and hates decaf and she didn't even notice I'd switched it
Results.Title: Excellent lovely taste

Results.ReviewText: Been drinking this for about a month now.  Really like depth of flavour and aroma, without bitterness.  Was really good value too.  Even tastes good if you don't catch kettle in time to avoid boiling water!

Results.ReviewText: I love Necafe Gold Decaff because it tastes every bit as great as Nescafe with caffeine but doesn't keep me up at night.  I have given it to friends and they couldn't taste the difference and loved it too.
